### 1. 회원가입 성공
POST http://localhost:10000/api/v1/auth/signup
Content-Type: application/json
X-Tenant-Code: alpha

{
  "email": "testuser1@example.com",
  "password": "Test1234!",
  "nickname": "테스트유저1",
  "phone": "01012345678"
}

### 2. 로그인 성공
POST http://localhost:10000/api/v1/auth/sign-in
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "testuser1@example.com",
  "password": "Test1234!"
}

> {%
  client.global.set("accessToken", response.body.data.accessToken);
  client.global.set("refreshToken", response.body.data.refreshToken);
%}

### asset 생성
POST http://localhost:10000/api/v1/assets
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
X-Tenant-Code: alpha

{
  "code": "sensor-001",
  "name": "센서 1호기",
  "externalKey": "ext-sensor-001",
  "description": "alpha tenant의 첫 번째 센서"
}

### asset 목록 조회
GET http://localhost:10000/api/v1/assets
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
X-Tenant-Code: alpha

### asset 단건 조회
GET http://localhost:10000/api/v1/assets/1
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
X-Tenant-Code: alpha